A '''flash''' was a physical ability of the [[Nosaurian/Legends|Nosaurians]], a species native to [[New Plympto/Legends|New Plympto]]. The flash was a brilliantly bright emission of phosphorescent light from Nosaurians' mouths. The ability was used as a method of communication and signalling among Nosaurian warriors. [[Bomo Greenbark]] used his flash ability to contact his comrades on New Plympto soon after encountering [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Dass Jennir]].

